bandmc: Fast Monte Carlo for BAND

Uses deuterium tagged DIS generator from Wim Cosyn

USER MUST SUPPLY INCLUSIVE ELECTRON SKIM ROOT FILE (SEE "REQUIRED DATA FILES" BELOW)

## Compiling 

In directory with "bandmc" repository:

$ mkdir build
$ ls
bandmc  build
$ cd build
$ cmake ../bandmc
$ make

## Running

$ ./bandmc [N events] [N background] [radiation on/off {1,0}] [smearing on/off {1,0}]

## Required data files

1. Data tables for generator (included in repository).

2. Inclusive electron skim ROOT file (NOT INCLUDED IN REPOSITORY).  You must move an inclusive electron skim ROOT file named "band_inclusive.root" to build/dat/
 
